            <p><add hand="#barker">Borrowing pair of pistols.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Foart Settlement Brasses</placeName> <date when="1823-11-05">5th Novr. 1823</date></p>
<p>Dear Sir&#8212;After My respects to you that I am well and hope you
enjoy the same blessing I am about to start in two or three days to
<placeName>New Orleans</placeName> and being in want of A pair of Pistols I beg the favour
of you to lend me yourse that are at <placeName><persName>Mr. Jones</persName>s</placeName>. I will take special
care of them and if you can let me have them I wish you to inform
<persName>Mr. Jones</persName> to let me have them&#8212;</p>

<p>and in so doing yon will much oblige Your Most obedient humble
servant</p>

<p><persName>Asa Mitchell</persName></p>

<p>[Addressed:]    <persName>Mr. Samuel Dixon</persName> <placeName>Brassos   </placeName>To the favor of <persName>Mr.
Jones</persName></p>

        </div1>
